 MTV VMA 与 Grandmaster Flash、Lil Wayne、Nicki Minaj 等一起庆祝嘻哈 50 周年https://www.nme.com/news/music/mtv-vmas-celebrates-50-years-hip-hop-grandmaster-flash-lil-wayne-nicki-minaj-3497079?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=mtv- vmas-庆祝嘻哈大师闪光 50 周年-lil-wayne-nicki-minajRhian Daly Wed, 13 Sep 2023 04:07:50 +0000 Music NewsNewsRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3497079 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/mtv-vmas-hip-hop.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="DMC、Nicki Minaj、LL Cool J" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/mtv-vmas-hip-hop.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/mtv-vmas-hip-hop-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/mtv-vmas-hip-hop-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/mtv-vmas-hip-hop-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/mtv-vmas-hip-hop-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/mtv-vmas-hip-hop-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Doug E. Fresh 和 The Get Fresh Crew、LL Cool J 和 Darryl “DMC” McDaniels 也出现在致敬中</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mtv-vmas-celebrates-50-years-hip-hop-grandmaster-flash-lil-wayne-nicki-minaj-3497079">MTV VMA 后庆祝嘻哈音乐 50 周年，Grandmaster Flash、Lil Wayne、Nicki Minaj 等人</a>首次在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上亮相。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/mtv-vmas-hip-hop.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="DMC、Nicki Minaj、LL Cool J" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/mtv-vmas-hip-hop.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/mtv-vmas-hip-hop-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/mtv-vmas-hip-hop-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/mtv-vmas-hip-hop-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/mtv-vmas-hip-hop-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/mtv-vmas-hip-hop-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 2023 年 MTV VMA 活动以庆祝嘻哈音乐 50 周年而告终，过去 50 年来该流派的一些先锋明星都有亮相。</p><p>这场表演是在该流派周年纪念日一个月后进行的，该流派被认为是 DJ Kool Herc 在布朗克斯的一场派对上创造了一种新的 DJ 方式而诞生的。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/here-are-all-the-winners-from-the-2023-mtv-vmas-3496804">以下是 2023 年 MTV VMA 的所有获奖者</a></strong></li></ul><p>闪电侠和速度与激情五人组以他们 1982 年的单曲“The Message”的演绎拉开了这场特别表演的序幕，然后交给 Doug E. Fresh 演绎了“The Show”的一个版本。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nicki-minaj">Nicki Minaj</a>通过《Itty Bitty Piggy》和《Red Ruby Da Sleaze》的混合曲将致敬带入了更现代的时代。</p><p>她还唱了 2015 年歌曲《Truffle Butter》中的一句歌词，她在其中夸口道：“<em>我现在肯定有大约一毫/而且我不是在谈论<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lil-wayne">Lil Wayne 的</a>唱片</em>。”当线路接近尾声时，节拍继续进入 Lil Wayne 的“A Milli”，说唱歌手拿起麦克风。 </p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f6a8.png" alt="🚨" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />警报，警报<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f6a8.png" alt="🚨" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p><p><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f5e3.png" alt="🗣" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f5e3.png" alt="🗣" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />大楼里的年轻人</p><p><a href="https://twitter.com/LilTunechi?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@LilTunechi</a>和<a href="https://twitter.com/NICKIMINAJ?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@NICKIMINAJ</a>都以嘻哈和遗产的名义用经典曲目祝福<a href="https://twitter.com/vmas?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@vmas</a>舞台！ <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/VMAS?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#VMAS</a> <a href="https://t.co/KOnpiCjgMG">pic.twitter.com/KOnpiCjgMG</a></p><p> - 穆拉 (@youngmoney) <a href="https://twitter.com/youngmoney/status/1701807856809377896?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 9 月 13 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>嘻哈庆祝活动在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ll-cool-j">LL Cool J</a>和 Run DMC 的 Darryl “DMC” McDaniels 的表演中结束。</p><p>在 VMA 的其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lil-wayne">Lil Wayne</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-lil-wayne-open-2023-mtv-vmas-3496833">以《Uproar》和《Kat Food》的表演</a>拉开了颁奖典礼的序幕。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-rodrigo">奥利维亚·罗德里戈（Olivia Rodrigo）</a>跟着他表演了《吸血鬼》和《让他回来！》，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/olivia-rodrigo-recreates-vampire-video-2023-mtv-vmas-3496836">重现了前一首歌曲的视频元素</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cardi-b">Cardi B</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/megan-thee-stallion">Megan Thee Stallion</a>还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cardi-b-megan-thee-stallion-bongos-live-premiere-2023-mtv-vmas-3496846">为他们的新合作歌曲“Bongos”进行了现场首演</a>，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/doja-cat">Doja Cat</a>则播放了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/doja-cat-storms-the-2023-mtv-vmas-with-scarlet-tracks-3496854">她即将推出的新专辑“Scarlet”中的三首歌曲</a>。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nicki-minaj">妮琪·米娜 (Nicki Minaj)</a>用她的表演 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nicki-minaj-previews-pink-friday-2-2023-mtv-vmas-3496858">预览了《粉红星期五 2》，并播放了一首未发行歌曲的片段</a>，黛米·<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/demi-lovato">洛瓦托 (Demi Lovato)</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-demi-lovato-bring-rock-versions-of-pop-hits-at-2023-mtv-vmas-3496862">在节目中带来了她的一些流行歌曲的摇滚版本</a>。</p><p> Stray Kids 首次亮相 MTV VMA， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/stray-kids-debut-mtv-vmas-appearance-s-class-performance-3496934">表演了《S-Class》的混音版</a>并获得了最佳 K-pop 奖。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shakira-crowdsurfs-as-she-collects-video-vanguard-award-at-2023-mtv-vmas-3496948">夏奇拉在获得视频先锋奖时进行了众筹</a>，成为第一位获得该奖项的南美艺术家。</p><p>与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tomorrow-x-together">Tomorrow X Together</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/anitta">Anitta</a>在颁奖典礼上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tomorrow-x-together-anitta-debut-back-for-more-mtv-vmas-3497000">首演了他们即将合作的歌曲《Back For More》</a> ，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fall-out-boy-updated-we-didnt-start-the-fire-2023-mtv-vmas-3497014">Fall Out Boy 则表演了他们对 Billy Joel 的《We Did not Start The Fire》的更新版本</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nsync-reportedly-set-to-reunite-at-2023-vmas-3496818">*NSYNC 十年来首次重聚，</a>为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>颁发了最佳流行音乐奖，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-says-she-and-jack-antonoff-will-continue-making-music-until-2089-at-2023-mtv-vmas-3496851">这位流行歌星在获得年度歌曲奖时赞扬了她的合作者杰克·安东诺夫</a>。 “我们将继续创作音乐直到 2089 年，”她开玩笑说。</p><p></p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mtv-vmas-celebrates-50-years-hip-hop-grandmaster-flash-lil-wayne-nicki-minaj-3497079">MTV VMA 后庆祝嘻哈音乐 50 周年，Grandmaster Flash、Lil Wayne、Nicki Minaj 等人</a>首次在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上亮相。</p> ;
 Jockstrap 宣布泰勒·斯凯 (Taylor Skye) 的水星提名歌曲《I Love You Jennifer B》的混音版https://www.nme.com/news/music/jockstrap-remixed-version-i-love-you-jennifer-b-taylor-skye-3497001?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=jockstrap-remixed-version-i-爱你-詹妮弗-B-泰勒-斯凯Tom DisalvoWed, 13 Sep 2023 04:06:54 +0000 Music NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3497001 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Taylor-Skye-and-Georgia-Ellery-of-Jockstrap.-Credit.-Eddie-Whelan-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Jockstrap 的泰勒·斯凯和乔治亚·埃勒里。信用。埃迪·惠兰 (1)" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Taylor-Skye-and-Georgia-Ellery-of-Jockstrap.-Credit.-Eddie-Whelan-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Taylor-Skye-and-Georgia-Ellery-of-Jockstrap.-Credit.-Eddie-Whelan-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Taylor-Skye-and-Georgia-Ellery-of-Jockstrap.-Credit.-Eddie-Whelan-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Taylor-Skye-and-Georgia-Ellery-of-Jockstrap.-Credit.-Eddie-Whelan-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Taylor-Skye-and-Georgia-Ellery-of-Jockstrap.-Credit.-Eddie-Whelan-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Taylor-Skye-and-Georgia-Ellery-of-Jockstrap.-Credit.-Eddie-Whelan-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>混音版的标题是“I&lt;3UQTINVU”，并附有刚刚发行的主打单曲</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jockstrap-remixed-version-i-love-you-jennifer-b-taylor-skye-3497001">Jockstrap 宣布泰勒·斯凯 (Taylor Skye) 获得 Mercury 提名的《I Love You Jennifer B》的混音版本</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Taylor-Skye-and-Georgia-Ellery-of-Jockstrap.-Credit.-Eddie-Whelan-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Jockstrap 的泰勒·斯凯和乔治亚·埃勒里。信用。埃迪·惠兰 (1)" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Taylor-Skye-and-Georgia-Ellery-of-Jockstrap.-Credit.-Eddie-Whelan-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Taylor-Skye-and-Georgia-Ellery-of-Jockstrap.-Credit.-Eddie-Whelan-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Taylor-Skye-and-Georgia-Ellery-of-Jockstrap.-Credit.-Eddie-Whelan-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Taylor-Skye-and-Georgia-Ellery-of-Jockstrap.-Credit.-Eddie-Whelan-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Taylor-Skye-and-Georgia-Ellery-of-Jockstrap.-Credit.-Eddie-Whelan-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Taylor-Skye-and-Georgia-Ellery-of-Jockstrap.-Credit.-Eddie-Whelan-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jockstrap">Jockstrap</a>宣布推出“I&lt;3UQTINVU”，这是他们首张专辑的混音版本，由 Taylor Skye 制作。<b></b></p><ul><li aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/jockstrap-i-love-you-jennifer-b-review-radar-3305709">Jockstrap – “I Love You Jennifer B”评论：神奇、迷人的首次亮相 – 也是年度最佳之一</a></b></li></ul><p>《I&lt;3UQTINVU》是《I Love You Cutie, I Envy You》的缩写，是对 Jockstrap 2022 年专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/jockstrap-i-love-you-jennifer-b-review-radar-3305709" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《I Love You Jennifer B》</a>的更新。混音版由 Skye 策划，她与 Georgia Ellery 一起组成了 Jockstrap 二人组之一。</p><p> Skye 为《I Love You Jennifer B》中的每首歌制作了混音版，以在专辑创作过程中保持灵感。斯凯在一份新闻声明中说：“其中一些混音版已经有近三年的历史了，有些只有六个月的历史。” “在混音专辑时这样做让我保持理智。”</p><p>定于 11 月 3 日发行的《I&lt;3UQTINVU》已与 IAN STARR 合作的主打单曲《Red Eye》进行了预览。新单曲附有由 Liam Noonan 拍摄的音乐视频，其中 STARR、Ellery 和 Skye 在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/boygenius-fred-again-primal-scream-to-headline-scotlands-connect-festival-2023-3407807" target="_blank" rel="noopener">今年的 Connect Festival</a>上表演。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Jockstrap 和 Taylor Skye - Red Eye ft. Ian Starr" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/MNMIFU1zogY?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “我喜欢创作能够突破我的声音和能量极限的歌曲，”斯塔尔说。 “我竭尽全力在《红眼》中打造出最疯狂的表演。” STARR 与其他特色艺术家 Ersatz、Coby Sey 等一起出现在《I&lt;3UQTINVU》中。</p><p>上个月，Jockstrap 凭借《I Love You Jennifer B》的作品入围 2023 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/mercury-prize">水星奖</a>入围名单，其他提名者包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arctic-monkeys">Arctic Monkeys</a> （ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/arctic-monkeys-the-car-review-3330197">《The Car》</a> ）、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/loyle-carner">Loyle Carner</a> （ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/loyle-carner-hugo-review-an-honest-unflashy-storyteller-3332632">《Hugo》</a> ）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-dean" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Olivia Dean</a> （《I Love You Jennifer B <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/olivia-dean-messy-review-debut-album-radar-3463419" target="_blank" rel="noopener">》）</a> 。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/olivia-dean-messy-review-debut-album-radar-3463419" target="_blank" rel="noopener">凌乱&#39;</a> ）等。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ezra-collective">Ezra Collective</a>最终凭借他们的第二张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ezra-collective-new-album-where-im-meant-to-be-sampa-the-great-life-goes-on-3296522" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《Where I&#39;m Meant To Be》</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ezra-collective-win-the-2023-mercury-prize-for-where-im-meant-to-be-3494841">获得了水星奖</a>。</p><p> “过去一年的反响非常好，”本月早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jockstrap-tease-new-collaborative-single-and-share-love-of-irish-folk-band-lankum-3495281">埃勒里在水星奖红地毯上告诉<em>《NME》</em></a> 。 “我们非常幸运。有一些伟大的节日，人们一起唱歌。无法要求更多。”</p><p> 《I Love You Jennifer B》去年 9 月发行后获得了<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/jockstrap-i-love-you-jennifer-b-review-radar-3305709" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>NME</em>的五星级评价</a>。 <i>NME</i>写道：“这对伦敦二人组对创新的不懈承诺将令新人和狂热粉丝兴奋不已。”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jockstrap-remixed-version-i-love-you-jennifer-b-taylor-skye-3497001">Jockstrap 宣布泰勒·斯凯 (Taylor Skye) 获得 Mercury 提名的《I Love You Jennifer B》的混音版本</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
